g TLA valid for next one year. While as per the own submissions of the RP the Trade mark was not even being used since 2018. II. As far as legal submissions were concerned, the order of the Adjudicating Authority dated 08.06.2021 is totally unreasoned and non- speaking order by citing multiple judgments as enunciated below:  
